        <h3>Schedule Design &amp; Analysis</h3>
        <p>Custom shift patterns that balance operational coverage, labor costs, fatigue management, and employee preferences. We don't pick from a menu — we design schedules around your specific coverage needs, demand patterns, and workforce reality.</p>
        <div class="service-note">8-hour, 12-hour, fixed, rotating, hybrid, semi-continuous, fly-in/fly-out, and more</div>
