        <p>Right-size your workforce for the schedule. We model staffing scenarios for hiring, attrition, and growth — so you know exactly how many people you need before committing to a pattern. No guesswork.</p>
        <div class="service-note">Headcount modeling, relief crew sizing, skill-balance analysis, vacancy planning</div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card" id="change-management">
