        <p>Our 103-question diagnostic survey captures what employees actually think — schedule preferences, overtime appetite, work-life balance priorities, and satisfaction levels. Every result is benchmarked against our proprietary normative database from hundreds of operations across 16 industries.</p>
        <div class="service-note">Full workforce surveys, normative benchmarking, demographic breakouts, trend tracking</div>
      </div>

